snippet.title: Party Hard 2 - Smell of Violence Trailer | October 25th on Steam
snippet.description:
🔪 Follow & Wishlist on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/572430/Party_Hard_2/
🔪 Download the DEMO - http://partyhard.game

Party Hard 2 is coming to Steam on October 25th, featuring 12 brand new levels rendered in a new engine, and a story centered around the interview with Darius' therapist. Stop the party by any means in this Stealth Strategy game!
